<br>
Zuldric level 5 Troll Basher <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uwandork.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wandor K</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/31/01 10:07:49 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: slam/bash</span><hr size=1> slam and bash are the same skill. work on kick. at 55 it also stuns. I know that is a long way from 5, but you don't want to get there and have a skill of 9. Try to keep ALL of your skills maxed or close to it at every level. You never know when you are going to get a killer weapon thats isnt 1hs or 2hs so better to have skill maxed. <p><span style="font-size: 14px; font-famliy: arial"><b>Wandor Kilbringer<br>Wizard of the 45th Conclave<br>Vini, Vidi, Nuki</b></span><br>
